    Memphis, TN Real Estate & Homes for Sale

    Homes for sale in Memphis, TN have a median listing price of $158,000. There are 123 active homes for sale in Memphis, TN. Some of the hottest neighborhoods near Memphis, TN are Sea Isle Park, Central Gardens, High Point Terrace, Colonial Acres, Wolfchase. You may also be interested in single family homes and condo/townhomes for sale in popular zip codes like 38117, 38111, or three bedroom homes for sale in neighboring cities, such as Germantown, Cordova, Bartlett, Collierville, Olive Branch.
